<section id="{{ filename }}" class="section">
    <div class="py-4 px-2 px-sm-4">
        <div class="section-heading mb-4">
            <a class="d-flex justify-content-between section-toggle text-decoration-none"
                data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#{{ filename }}Collapse" role="button" 
                aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="{{ filename }}Collapse">
                <h2 class="display-6 w-100 d-flex m-0">
                    Rail fence cipher
                </h2>
                <span class="text-light px-1 border rounded align-self-end toggle-button">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up lh-base"></i>
                </span>
            </a>
            <hr>
            <p class="px-2">
                Also known as the Zig Zag cipher, takes its name from the way in which the encryption is performed - in analogy to a fence built with horizontal rails. Below is an example using 3 rails, more rails equals more complexity and makes it harder to decode without the correct number of rails.
                There is more information available on the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rail_fence_cipher" class="text-convrtr">Rail fence cipher</a> Wikipedia page. 
            </p>
            <p class="px-2">
                <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 my-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">
                    WE ARE DISCOVERED. RUN AT ONCE.
                </code>
                <code class="d-flex px-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2" style="
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            ">
    W . . . E . . . C . . . R . . . U . . . O . . . 
    . E . R . D . S . O . E . E . R . N . T . N . E 
    . . A . . . I . . . V . . . D . . . A . . . C . 
            </code>
            <code class="d-inline-flex px-2 my-2 bg-success bg-opacity-10 border border-success border-opacity-10 rounded-2">
                WECRUO ERDSOEERNTNE AIVDAC
            </code>

            </p>
            
        </div>
        <div class="collapse" id="{{ filename }}Collapse">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card">
                    <span class="card-label visually-hidden">Rail fence cipher</span>
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <textarea placeholder="Example: HELLO WORLD â†’ HOLELWRDLO" title="Encrypt / Decrypt Rail fence string" rows="6" id="{{ filename }}Text" class="form-control {{ filename }}-cipher" autocomplete="off"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer py-3">
                        <div class="text-center mb-4 g-0">
                            <div class="row row-cols-2 g-md-0 gx-0 gy-2">
                                <div class="col col-12 col-md-auto">
                                    <div class="input-group w-auto">
                                        <label class="input-group-text" id="{{ filename }}AmountLabel" for="{{ filename }}Amount"><span class="visually-hidden">Number of </span>Rails</label>
                                        <input type="number" class="form-control" id="{{ filename }}Amount" autocomplete="off" min="2" value="2">
                                        <button class="btn btn-convrtr" type="button" id="{{ filename }}Encrypt">Encrypt</button>
                                        <button class="btn btn-outline-convrtr" type="button" id="{{ filename }}Decrypt">Decrypt</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col d-flex flex-fill justify-content-end">
                                    {% include "components/select-copy-dl" %}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                        <div id="{{ filename }}Results" class="data-to-copy active convrtr-results"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>